        "desc": "被「往生堂」请来的神秘客人，知识渊博，对各种事物都颇有见地。",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/22/327628065/95b4b908502d2ab048428734f37ad3a2_212527091962952135.png",
